ED_Title: Comprehensive implementation  of and follow-up to the Vienna Declaration and Programme of Action
ED_DecisionText: At its 54th plenary meeting, on 15 December 2022, the General Assembly took note of the report of the Third Committee.  (Footnote: A/77/463/Add.4.)
ED_Disclaimer: The final version of decisions adopted during the main part of the session will be contained in document A/77/49 (Vol. II) after editorial review.
